Description.Text: the Maya Caribe Hotel-All Inclusive is situated on the northern stretch of Cancun's white-sand beach among a lush palm grove and offers the culture and natural wonders of Mexico's Yucatan Peninsula in a serene, exotic garden and private beachfront setting. 1108GAB
This All Inclusive hotel is situated within close proximity to the club scene and shopping district of Cancun. 25 minutes from the international airport and 10 minutes from downtown.
The three star hotel has got 28 rooms and 12 bungalows (ocean view, garden view. pool view) Room are in good condition and are medium in size.

Xcaret Casual Buffet offers daily Breakfast from 07:00 to 11:00hrs, lunch from 13:00 to 15:00hrs and dinner from 18:00 to 22:30hrs La Parrilla Snack Bar: Snacks available from 11:00 to 17:00hrs Xel-Ha Specialty: dinner from 17:00 to 22:00hrs (service available Mon/Wed/Fri)
